data.description: Setup a Showing Today to see this Custom Built 2 Story Home in Chadwick Village! This 5 bedroom, 3 Full bath home on Half Acre has No HOAs! Chill in the Lounge Room just off the Foyer and grab a glass. Updated Kitchen/Granite Countertops that Opens up to the Family Room with Fireplace for those cool nights! Formal Dining Room, 3 bedrooms and 2 Full Baths on Main. 2 bedrooms and 1 Full Bath on Upper Level. Massive Loft for Entertainment and relaxation! Extra Storage Room and Above Garage storage area on 2nd level just off the Loft.  2 Car Garage. Enclosed Glass Patio Adjoins the Large Hardscaped Outdoor Entertaining!!  Big Backyard in this well established neighborhood. Also, within walking distance to Lebanon High and all the Amenities at Memorial Park!!  Make this Beautiful House your Forever Home!!!!!!.....Seller is offering Concessions at Closing!!!!!!!... Setup a Walk through with an agent today for all the Details!
